    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 56px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Махфий васиятноманинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#2}Махфий васиятнома тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни ушбу васиятномани мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси,</span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Васиятномани тасдиқлаётган нотариал идора манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">даги </span><span class=\"structures structure-21 structure-23\" style=\"className:21 23; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}давлат нотариал идорасининг рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21} </span><span class=\"structures structure-21 structure-21\" style=\"className:21 21; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}давлат нотариал идораси</span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#22}хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариуc</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Нотариус тўғрисида маълумот ва Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да васият қилувчининг хоҳиш-иродасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси қонун ҳужжатларига асосан тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ушбу васиятномани фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Васиятномани имзолаган фуқаронинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ҳақиқий саналмаслик хавфи остида ўз қўли билан ёзди ва имзолади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васиятнома менинг ҳузуримда ва гувоҳлар – </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Биринчи гувоҳнинг яшаш манзили </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Биринчи гувоҳнинг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сонли уйда яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Биринчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#12}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#13}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сонли уйда яшовчи фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> иштирокида хатжилдга солинди. Хатжилд елимланиб, муҳрланди ва гувоҳлар томонидан менинг ҳузуримда имзоланди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васиятнома солинган хатжилд васият қилувчи, гувоҳлар ва нотариус иштирокида бошқа хатжилдга солинди ва елимланди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васият қилувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Васиятномани имзолаган фуқаронинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ва гувоҳлар </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Биринчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#14}Иккинчи гувоҳнинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг шахслари аниқланди ва уларнинг муомалага лаёқатлиликлари текширилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Шахсий мулоқот давомида васият қилувчининг ва гувоҳларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизлигига шубҳа туғилмади ва ушбу нотариал ҳаракатни амалга ошириш даврида нотариал идорада уларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизликлари ҳақида ҳеч қандай маълумотлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Васиятнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Васиятномани тасдиқлаётган нотариал идора манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5} Нотариус тўғрисида маълумот ва Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">(</span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#5}Нотариус тўғрисида маълумот ва Ф.И.</span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">соат </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Васиятнома тасдиқланган вақт</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> да тасдиқланди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Реестрга қайд қилинган рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Давлат божи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Давлат божи миқдори </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Нотариус тўғрисида маълумот ва Ф.И.О</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p></p>\n</div></div>",
